dde-dock-netspeed-plugin (1.4.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Full auto-update via GitHub Releases API
  * Detect new version on startup and via right-click menu
  * QMessageBox confirmation dialog before update
  * Download .deb in background with progress notification
  * Install via pkexec + dpkg (polkit authorization dialog)
  * Auto-restart dde-shell after successful installation
  * Show current version in right-click menu

